name: Stupid Cars
summary:
These Vehicles are… STUPID!

Speed them up and Slow them down using Hand Tracking or Controllers. But be careful, these vehicles can’t stop… 

2 Action Packed Game Modes

Multiplayer - Dumb vs Dumber** - Invite a friend to 3 minutes of Madness. Highest Score Wins!

{"height":1440,"type":"image","width":2560}
Arcade**  - Beat your top score, but be careful, if there’s a collision, it’s all over!

Designed to be one of the most challenging "One More Go" games...
